{"type": "article", "id": 8768, "title": "「 A’  设计大奖赛」之 Ane Stool 椅子", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-22T07:27:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235037lFOUvPdB3Vtw5AYy.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t家具设计师 Troy Backhouse 设计的这一款椅子名叫 “Ane Stool”，材料上采取的橡木，通过 CNC 切割技术，让整个椅子看上去充满流动的韵律，而连接部分采用的是低碳钢，和优雅的木头配合得十分得体，而造型独特别致，个性十足。<a href=\"https://competition.adesignaward.com/design.php?ID=39082\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235035ZlG6Px4KvS3RW2Dw.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.77592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052350368yrhpwi7RA0eZ1kO.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.69351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052350363oJXfUMAshPEzCgx.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.76851852\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235037vmQ7V4hSOMxp8PN2.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.78611111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}